  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Hot &amp; cold buffet breakfast (served 7am-10am) </li>
<li>Excellent four course evening meal with three choices of main course, plus salad buffet</li>
<li>On Tuesdays dinner is a small buffet and hot dish</li>
<li>Weekly gala dinner and Mediterranean dinner</li>
<li>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included</li>
<li>Smart casual wear required at meal times (no ski clothes)</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
