  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>In a quiet yet central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/3c3783ff0696436cb752c8195e705dec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3c3783ff0696436cb752c8195e705dec}" title="Ischgl">Ischgl</a> just 2 minutes to the Pardatschgrat cable car you will find the extravagant design of Hotel Solaria. Well known for its friendly and welcoming hospitality there is a warm atmosphere here.</span></p>
<h2><span>A relaxing stay</span></h2>
<p><span>After a day on the slopes unwind in the extensive spa facilities featuring an indoor pool, sauna, steam room and gym. </span>The hotel specialises in cosmetic &amp; massage treatments. </p>
<h2><span>Traditional alpine bar</span></h2>
<p><span>Be sure to visit the hotel's </span>lovely bar in the style of a traditional Alpine lodge.</p>
<p>Appetising themed dinners throughout the week ensure you can enjoy a selection of both regional and international dishes. All served up in the ornate dining room with attractive traditional architecture. </p>
<p>Bedrooms are well thought out, with modern design, great attention to detail and unique features.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Solaria making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"> </p>]]></description>
